          <heading>Committee process</heading>
          <para>
            <text>The Walking Access Bill was referred to the committee on 15 April 2008. The closing date for submissions was 21 May 2008. We received and considered 136 submissions from interested groups and individuals, of which 38 were heard.</text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>We received advice from the Ministry of Agriculture and Forestry and the Department of Conservation.</text>
          </para>
